the arithmetic–geometric mean, "agm".

It is possible to use this fact to construct <a href="fast%20algorithms">fast algorithms</a> for calculating <a href="elementary%20function">elementary</a> <a href="transcendental%20function">transcendental function</a>s and some classical constants, in particular, the constant <a href="pi"></a>.

For example, according to the Gauss–<a href="Eugene%20Salamin%20%28mathematician%29">Salamin</a> formula:

